simple twitter client
シンプルなTwitterのクライアント

for my study about python
pythonの勉強用

* set up steps
* first, you register your own twitter aplication details https://apps.twitter.com/
* second you get your keys
** consumer_key
** consumer_secret
** access_token
** access_token_secret
* third, you create "twitter_config.ini" file and write like this
[twitter_app_config]
consumer_key=XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
consumer_secret=YYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYY
access_token=ZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZ
access_token_secret=XYZXYZXYZXYZXYZXYZ

usage
sample is here
import twitter_api
obj =twitter_api.twitter_api()
obj.post_tweet("hello! twitter world!!")

